'''戈登·莱特福特'''（Gordon Lightfoot，{{bd|1938年|11月17日}}），[[加拿大|加拿大]]唱作人，在[[民谣|民谣]]，[[民谣摇滚|民谣摇滚]]，[[乡村音乐|乡村音乐]]领域获得了国际性的成功，并被认为是在1960年代和1970年代帮助定义了流行民谣。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/arts/story/2012/02/21/gordon-lightfoot.html | work=CBC News | title=Gordon Lightfoot to join U.S. Songwriters Hall of Fame – Arts & Entertainment – CBC News | accessdate=2014-06-04 | archive-date=2013-02-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130224154444/http://www.cbc.ca/news/arts/story/2012/02/21/gordon-lightfoot.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>他常被认为是加拿大最杰出的歌曲作者。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.winnipegfreepress.com/opinion/columnists/if-you-could-read-his-mind-134812923.html |title=If you could read his mind |author=Mayes, Alison |date=December 1, 2011 |publisher=''Winnipeg Free Press.com'' |accessdate=2011-12-26 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225014557/https://www.winnipegfreepress.com/opinion/columnists/if-you-could-read-his-mind-134812923.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

莱特福特的作品包括"For Lovin' Me", "Early Morning Rain", "Steel Rail Blues", "Ribbon of Darkness"（曾荣登美国乡村乐排行榜首位）<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/gordon-lightfoot-p2053 |title=Gordon Lightfoot | Music Biography, Credits and Discography |publisher=AllMusic |date=1938-11-17 |accessdate=2014-04-19 |archive-date=2011-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111211064750/http://allmusic.com/artist/gordon-lightfoot-p2053 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以[[1967年底特律骚乱|1967年底特律骚乱]]为素材的"Black Day In July"在1960年代为他带来了国际声誉。他1970年代的一些歌曲也登上了国际歌曲排行榜，比如"If You Could Read My Mind" (1970) (美国排行榜第5), "Sundown" (1974), "Carefree Highway" (1974), "Rainy Day People" (1975)，这3首都曾登上首位，以及"The Wreck of the Edmund Fitzgerald" (1976)（第2位）。<ref name="bill">{{cite book|title=The Billboard Book of  Hits |ISBN=0-8230-8285-7|author=Adam White & Fred Bronson|publisher=Billboard Books|year=1988}}</ref>

